<h2>Mutual Fund Calculator</h2>

<p>
Estimate the future value of your regular mutual fund investment using this free calculator. Results are estimates only and do not guarantee future returns.
</p>

<label><strong>Monthly Investment (₹)</strong></label>

<input
type="number"
id="sip"
placeholder="Example: 5000">

<br><br>

<label><strong>Investment Period (Years)</strong></label>

<input
type="number"
id="years"
placeholder="Example: 20">

<br><br>

<label><strong>Expected Annual Return (%)</strong></label>

<input
type="number"
id="rate"
placeholder="Example: 12">

<br><br>
<div class="article-buttons">

<button onclick="calculateMF()">
📈 Calculate
</button>

<button onclick="resetMF()">
🔄 Reset
</button>

</div>

<br>

<div class="article-box" id="resultBox" style="display:none;">

<h3>Calculation Result</h3>

<p><strong>Total Investment:</strong></p>

<h2 id="investedAmount">₹0</h2>

<p><strong>Estimated Returns:</strong></p>

